<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Pascal Gagnon — Économie, Énergie &amp; PME du Québec</title>
<meta name="description" content="Pascal Gagnon observe l'économie, l'énergie et les PME du Québec depuis le terrain. Directeur de compte Desjardins Entreprise, conseiller municipal Roberval.">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;0,900;1,400&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
*, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
:root {
  --noir: #0a0a0a;
  --creme: #f5f0e8;
  --bleu: #0063b2;
  --bleu-clair: #4d92c9;
  --bleu-pale: #e6eff7;
  --gris: #6b6b6b;
  --gris-clair: #d4cfc6;
  --max: 1200px;
}
html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
body { background: var(--creme); color: var(--noir); font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-weight: 300; overflow-x: hidden; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.7; }

/* ── NAV ── */
nav { position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 100; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding: 1.4rem 4rem; background: rgba(245,240,232,0.96); backdrop-filter: blur(12px); border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,99,178,0.15); }
.nav-logo { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--noir); text-decoration: none; }
.nav-logo span { color: var(--bleu); }
.nav-links { display: flex; gap: 2.5rem; list-style: none; }
.nav-links a { font-size: 0.78rem; letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--gris); text-decoration: none; transition: color 0.3s; }
.nav-links a:hover { color: var(--bleu); }
.nav-cta { font-size: 0.78rem; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; padding: 0.6rem 1.6rem; border: 1px solid var(--bleu); color: var(--bleu); text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.3s; }
.nav-cta:hover { background: var(--bleu); color: #fff; }
@media (max-width: 768px) { nav { padding: 1rem 1.5rem; } .nav-links { display: none; } }

/* ── HERO ── */
.hero { min-height: 80vh; display: flex; align-items: center; padding-top: 80px; background: var(--creme); }
.hero-left { display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; padding: 6rem 4rem; max-width: 820px; }
@media (max-width: 768px) { .hero-left { padding: 3rem 1.5rem; } }
.hero-eyebrow { font-size: 0.72rem; letter-spacing: 0.25em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--bleu-clair); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.8rem; }
.hero-eyebrow::before { content: ''; display: block; width: 40px; height: 1px; background: var(--bleu-clair); }
.hero-title { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 4.5vw, 5rem); font-weight: 900; line-height: 1.0; margin-bottom: 0.3rem; color: var(--noir); letter-spacing: -0.02em; }
.hero-title em { font-style: italic; color: var(--bleu); }
.hero-subtitle { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 1.6vw, 1.4rem); font-weight: 400; font-style: italic; color: var(--gris); margin-bottom: 1.8rem; margin-top: 0.5rem; }
.hero-verticaux { font-size: 0.72rem; letter-spacing: 0.16em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--bleu-clair); margin-bottom: 2.8rem; line-height: 1.5; }
.hero-actions { display: flex; gap: 1.2rem; align-items: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
.btn-primary { background: var(--bleu); color: #fff; padding: 1rem 2.2rem; font-size: 0.82rem; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.3s; font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; border: 1px solid var(--bleu); }
.btn-primary:hover { background: var(--noir); border-color: var(--noir); color: #fff; }
.btn-secondary { font-size: 0.82rem; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--gris); text-decoration: none; transition: color 0.3s; }
.btn-secondary:hover { color: var(--bleu); }

/* ── DIVIDER ── */
.section-divider { height: 1px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--bleu-clair), transparent); margin: 0 4rem; opacity: 0.4; }

/* ── ARTICLE VEDETTE ── */
.article-central { padding: 7rem 4rem; max-width: var(--max); margin: 0 auto; }
@media (max-width: 768px) { .article-central { padding: 4rem 1.5rem; } }
.section-label { font-size: 0.68rem; letter-spacing: 0.28em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--bleu-clair); display: block; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
.central-inner { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 2fr; gap: 5rem; align-items: start; }
@media (max-width: 768px) { .central-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2rem; } }
.central-tag { font-size: 0.68rem; letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--bleu); display: block; margin-bottom: 0.8rem; }
.central-temps { font-size: 0.82rem; color: var(--gris); }
.central-content h2 { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3vw, 2.8rem); font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.15; margin-bottom: 1.4rem; letter-spacing: -0.01em; }
.central-content h2 em { font-style: italic; color: var(--bleu); }
.central-chapeau { font-size: 1.15rem; line-height: 1.85; color: #3a3a3a; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
.central-lien { font-size: 0.78rem; letter-spacing: 0.14em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--bleu); text-decoration: underline; text-underline-offset: 4px; transition: color 0.2s; }
.central-lien:hover { color: var(--noir); }

/* ── ARTICLES RÉCENTS ── */
.articles-recents { padding: 0 4rem 7rem; max-width: var(--max); margin: 0 auto; }
@media (max-width: 768px) { .articles-recents { padding: 0 1.5rem 4rem; } }
.articles-header { display: flex; align-items: baseline; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 3rem; border-top: 1px solid var(--gris-clair); padding-top: 2.5rem; }
.articles-header h2 { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 1.4rem; font-weight: 700; }
.voir-tout { font-size: 0.72rem; letter-spacing: 0.14em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--bleu); text-decoration: none; transition: letter-spacing 0.3s; }
.voir-tout:hover { letter-spacing: 0.22em; }
.articles-grille { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 3rem; }
@media (max-width: 768px) { .articles-grille { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2rem; } }
.article-card { display: flex; flex-direction: column; border-top: 2px solid var(--gris-clair); padding-top: 1.8rem; transition: border-color 0.25s; }
.article-card:hover { border-color: var(--bleu); }
.card-vertical { font-size: 0.65rem; letter-spacing: 0.22em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--bleu); margin-bottom: 0.8rem; }
.card-titre { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.25; color: var(--noir); text-decoration: none; display: block; margin-bottom: 0.9rem; transition: color 0.2s; }
.article-card:hover .card-titre { color: var(--bleu); }
.card-extrait { font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; color: #4a4a4a; margin-bottom: 1.2rem; flex: 1; }
.card-meta { font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--gris); letter-spacing: 0.04em; }

/* ── INFOLETTRE ── */
.newsletter { padding: 7rem 4rem; border-top: 1px solid var(--gris-clair); }
@media (max-width: 768px) { .newsletter { padding: 4rem 1.5rem; } }
.newsletter-inner { max-width: 520px; margin: 0 auto; text-align: center; }
.nl-h2 { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 2.6vw, 2.3rem); font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.2; color: var(--noir); margin-bottom: 1rem; letter-spacing: -0.01em; }
.nl-h2 em { font-style: italic; color: var(--bleu); }
.nl-desc { font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.85; color: var(--gris); margin-bottom: 2.4rem; }
.nl-form { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.8rem; }
.nl-form input { background: transparent; border: 1px solid var(--gris-clair); padding: 0.95rem 1.2rem; font-size: 1rem; color: var(--noir); font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; outline: none; transition: border-color 0.2s; text-align: center; }
.nl-form input::placeholder { color: var(--gris-clair); }
.nl-form input:focus { border-color: var(--bleu); }
.nl-form button { background: var(--bleu); color: #fff; border: none; padding: 1rem 1.2rem; font-size: 0.78rem; letter-spacing: 0.14em; text-transform: uppercase; font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.25s; }
.nl-form button:hover { background: var(--noir); }
.nl-note { font-size: 0.72rem; color: var(--gris-clair); margin-top: 0.6rem; }

/* ── FOOTER ── */
footer { background: var(--noir); padding: 2.5rem 4rem; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 1.5rem; }
@media (max-width: 768px) { footer { padding: 2rem 1.5rem; flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; } }
.footer-logo { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; color: rgba(245,240,232,0.5); text-decoration: none; }
.footer-logo span { color: var(--bleu-clair); }
.footer-links { display: flex; gap: 2rem; list-style: none; flex-wrap: wrap; }
.footer-links a { font-size: 0.72rem; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; color: rgba(245,240,232,0.3); text-decoration: none; transition: color 0.2s; }
.footer-links a:hover { color: var(--bleu-clair); }
.footer-ref { font-size: 0.65rem; color: rgba(245,240,232,0.18); font-style: italic; }
.footer-copy { font-size: 0.65rem; color: rgba(245,240,232,0.2); }

/* ── ANIMATIONS ── */
.reveal { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(24px); transition: opacity 0.7s ease, transform 0.7s ease; }
.reveal.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav>
  <a href="/" class="nav-logo">Pascal<span>.</span>Gagnon</a>
  <ul class="nav-links">
    <li><a href="/economie-energie/">Économie &amp; Énergie</a></li>
    <li><a href="/terrain-pme/">Terrain PME</a></li>
    <li><a href="/marketing-numerique/">Marketing numérique</a></li>
  </ul>
  <a href="#newsletter" class="nav-cta">Infolettre</a>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-left">
    <p class="hero-eyebrow">Directeur de compte Desjardins Entreprise · Conseiller municipal, Roberval</p>
    <h1 class="hero-title">Le Lac-Saint-Jean<br><em>se transforme.</em></h1>
    <p class="hero-subtitle">J'observe depuis l'intérieur, j'écris ce que je vois.</p>
    <p class="hero-verticaux">Économie &amp; Énergie &nbsp;·&nbsp; Terrain PME &nbsp;·&nbsp; Marketing numérique</p>
    <div class="hero-actions">
      <a href="/blog/" class="btn-primary">Lire les articles</a>
      <a href="/a-propos/" class="btn-secondary">À propos →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="section-divider"></div>

<!-- ARTICLE VEDETTE -->
<section class="article-central reveal">
  <span class="section-label">À lire en premier ——</span>
  <div class="central-inner">
    <div>
      <span class="central-tag">◆ {{ articles.featured.vertical }}</span>
      <span class="central-temps">Lecture : ~{{ articles.featured.reading_time }}</span>
    </div>
    <div class="central-content">
      <h2>{{ articles.featured.title }}</h2>
      <p class="central-chapeau">{{ articles.featured.chapeau }}</p>
      <a href="{{ articles.featured.url if articles.featured.url else '/articles/' + articles.featured.slug + '/' }}" class="central-lien">Lire l'article →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="section-divider"></div>

<!-- ARTICLES RÉCENTS -->
<section class="articles-recents reveal">
  <div class="articles-header">
    <h2>Articles récents</h2>
    <a href="/blog/" class="voir-tout">Tous les articles →</a>
  </div>
  <div class="articles-grille">
    {% for article in articles.recent %}
    <article class="article-card">
      <span class="card-vertical">{{ article.vertical }}</span>
      <a href="{{ article.url if article.url else '/articles/' + article.slug + '/' }}" class="card-titre">{{ article.title }}</a>
      <p class="card-extrait">{{ article.chapeau }}</p>
      <span class="card-meta">{{ article.date }} &nbsp;·&nbsp; {{ article.reading_time }}</span>
    </article>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>

<div class="section-divider"></div>

<!-- INFOLETTRE -->
<section class="newsletter reveal" id="newsletter">
  <div class="newsletter-inner">
    <span class="section-label">Infolettre ——</span>
    <h2 class="nl-h2">Ce que j'observe sur le terrain,<em> une fois par mois.</em></h2>
    <p class="nl-desc">Pas de contenu recyclé. Pas de promotion. Des analyses qui prennent position sur l'économie, l'énergie et les PME du Québec.</p>
    <div class="nl-form">
      <input type="text" placeholder="Votre prénom">
      <input type="email" placeholder="Votre courriel">
      <button type="button">Je m'abonne</button>
      <p class="nl-note">Désabonnement en un clic. Conforme à la Loi 25.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- FOOTER -->
<footer>
  <a href="/" class="footer-logo">Pascal<span>.</span>Gagnon</a>
  <ul class="footer-links">
    <li><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/pascalgagnon/" target="_blank">LinkedIn</a></li>
    <li><a href="/blog/">Articles</a></li>
    <li><a href="https://histoire.pascalgagnon.ca/">Histoire · Saints</a></li>
    <li><a href="/a-propos/">À propos</a></li>
    <li><a href="mailto:pascal@pascalgagnon.ca">Contact</a></li>
  </ul>
  <span class="footer-ref">Ibn Khaldoun · Biophysique économique · Terrain québécois</span>
  <p class="footer-copy">© 2026 Pascal Gagnon</p>
</footer>

<script>
const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
  entries.forEach(e => { if (e.isIntersecting) e.target.classList.add('visible'); });
}, { threshold: 0.1 });
document.querySelectorAll('.reveal').forEach(el => observer.observe(el));
</script>
</body>
</html>
